  notes:
    - "Wave 682 (re3526): __set_name__, __init_subclass__, __class_getitem__ dict-presence checks for re types."
    - "All values false — re.Pattern, re.Match, and re.RegexFlag do not implement class creation hooks or generic parameterization."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

